(30, 10, 18, 'CET ENZYMATIC TOOTHPASTE KIT', 'VIRBAC', '&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px; font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold;\\&quot;&gt;Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;This product provides a complete kit with everything pet owners need to start a program of regular oral hygiene for their dog.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;Convenient and complete starter dental care kit designed for dog owners to use at home. Contains C.E.T. Fingerbrush with C.E.T. Enzymatic Toothpaste and C.E.T. Dual-Ended Toothbrush.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;Each kit contains:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;C.E.T. Fingerbrush, an ideal beginner toothbrush to help acquaint dogs and their owners with the toothbrushing exper