(53, 9, 15, 'BIOSPOTIX CAT SPRAY 500ml', 'BIOGANCE', '&lt;p style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 25px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 10pt;\\&quot;&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;text-align: justify;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;Fleas and ticks love your cat for the wrong reason, and you can help to protect your cat from these unwanted guests! Biospotix Cat Spray is a natural solution that guards your feline friend from external parasites like fleas, ticks and mosquitoes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;It contains Geraniol which naturally repels pests by dehydrating and stifling them, and this can be used regularly to avoid new infestations. The spray helps to create a protective film on the surface of the skin and offers effective protection for up to 48 hours.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;- Easy-to-use spray which can be used regularly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;- Contains geraniol which naturally repels