(54, 9, 15, 'FLEAS AWAY CAT SHAMPOO 250ml', 'BIOGANCE', '&lt;p style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 25px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 13px;\\&quot;&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;Flea, flea, go away! Never, ever come again!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13px;\\&quot;&gt;Biogance Fleas Away Repellent Cat Shampoo is formulated to repel fleas, ticks and external parasites. This double-action, pH-balanced shampoo is enriched with essential oils to protect the coat and prevent unwanted intruders. It gently cleanses the coat and does not contain any parabens. This product is also suitable for kittens.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13px;\\&quot;&gt;- Formulated with essential oils&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13px;\\&quot;&gt;- Repels fleas, ticks and external parasites&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13px;\\&quot;&gt;- Gently cleanses, nourishes and hydrates the coat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;sp