(125, 7, 29, 'TURTLE CONDITIONER', 'NUTRAFIN (TP)', '&lt;p style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 25px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 10pt;\\&quot;&gt;Features:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;Specifically made for turtles and terrapins, Nutrafin Turtle Conditioner-plus calcium- helps keep water from going acidic, while the calcium that is released as the block dissolves aids in preventing softening of the turtle\\&#039;s shell.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;-Suitable for turtles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;-Slowly releases calcium to help prevent soft shells, and harden outer shells&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;-Helps keep water from becoming acidic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold;\\&quot;&gt;Ingredients:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;Calcium Sulfate (24%), Spirulina, Magnesium Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Thiamine Hydrochloride.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold;\\&quot;&gt;Analysis :&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Calcium (min.)&lt;span style=\\&quot;white-space: pre;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;22.0%, Calcium (max.) 26.0%, Thiamine (min.)&lt;span style=\\&quot;white-space: pre;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;2,100 mg/kg&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 10pt;\\&quot;&gt;Size:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 10pt;\\&quot;&gt;15g&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 10pt;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 10pt;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold;\\&quot;&gt;Usage Guideline:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\\&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 13.3333px;\\&quot;&gt;Place Nutrafin Turtle Conditioner into the water contained in the turtle bowl or aquarium. The block will immediately begin to dissolve. This neutralizes acids released into the water by the turtle and also conditions the water. Some water should be changed daily in turtle bowls and aquariums to ensure good water quality and increase the effectiveness of Nutrafin Turtle Conditioner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, '2023-10-03 22:24:49'),
(126, 7, 29, 'Turtle Health Block - 20g', 'Aquatopia', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;﻿&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\\&quot;desc-head\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-bottom: 30px; display: block; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;DESCRIPTION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;wrap-prod-desc\\&quot; style=\\&quot;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;This is a 20g Aquatopia Turtle Health Block. The Turtle Health Block beneficial vitamins and minerals into the water that your pet lives. Calcium, along with vitamin D3 and other minerals help prevent shell softening, which may be caused by the water becoming acidic. This block acts as a pH buffer, reducing acid while also neutralising ammonia that is produced by animal waste. Natural sunlight or suitable artificial lighting are essential for the well being and shell hardness of your turtle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=\\&quot;line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 10px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Directions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\\&quot;&gt;Please the complete block into the water of your terrarium or aquarium. One block will treat up to 120 lites of water.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=\\&quot;line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 10px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;How to Calculate Tank Capacity&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom