(127, 7, 29, 'Liquid Calcium + Magnesium Supplement - 120ml', 'Exo Terra', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=\\&quot;desc-head\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; display: block; font-family: Verdana; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=\\&quot;#000000\\&quot;&gt;DESCRIPTION&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=\\&quot;wrap-prod-desc\\&quot; style=\\&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Work Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=\\&quot;#000000\\&quot;&gt;This is a 120ml Exo Terra Liquid Calcium - Magnesium Supplement for Reptiles and Amphibians. It will provide your reptile with essential calcium needed for their health. This supplement will help maintain bone health and supports calcium metabolism.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=\\&quot;line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=\\&quot;#000000\\&quot;&gt;About This Exo Terra Reptile Supplement&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul style=\\&quot;margin-bottom: 10px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font color=\\&quot;#000000\\&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;Size:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;120ml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font color=\\&quot;#000000\\&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=\\&quot;font-weight: bold;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;Type:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;\\&quot